
'''Marie Claire Mukasine''' (wavutse 1959) ni umunyamategeko [[Rwanda|w'umunyarwandakazi]], umunyapolitiki n'umukozi wa Leta. Kuva mu 2011 kugeza 2019 yari umwe mu bagize Sena y'u Rwanda, kandi yabaye umunyamabanga uhoraho muri [[Ministry of Infrastructure (Rwanda) - MININFRA|Minisiteri y'Ibikorwa Remezo]] mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref name="WhoIsWho">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/35739</ref> <ref>http://haguruka.org.rw/</ref> Muri 2020 yagizwe Perezida wa Komisiyo y'igihugu ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu mu [[Rwanda]] (NHCR)<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/35739</ref><ref name=":0" />.

== Uburezi ==
Mukasine afite impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu by'amategeko, impamyabumenyi ebyiri z'icyiciro cya kabiri mu micungire n'imiyoborere , na PhD mu by'amategeko. <ref name="WhoIsWho" /> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/mukasine-named-new-chairperson-human-rights-commission</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mukasine yagiye akora mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuyobozi nk'umunyamabanga nshingwabikorwa wa Haguruka, umuryango utabara imbabare uharanira no kurengera uburenganzira bw'umugore n'abana.  <ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=ynL_aOLfomsC&q=Marie+Mukasine</ref> <ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=k05FtHAc50AC&dq=Marie+Mukasine&pg=PA85</ref> Yabaye umunyamabanga uhoraho muri Minisiteri y’uburinganire n’iterambere ry’umuryango mu [[Rwanda]]. Yabaye kandi umuyobozi mukuru wa [[Rwanda]] Investment Group(RIG), n’umuyobozi mukuru w’isosiyete y’ubwishingizi Sonarwa. Muri 2013 yari umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubwishingizi . <ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=CQWhAQAAQBAJ&dq=Marie+Mukasine&pg=PA1368</ref>

Mu 2011, Mukasine yatorewe kujya muri Sena y'u [[Rwanda]] nk'uhagarariye [[Intara y'amajyepfo|Intara y'Amajyepfo]],  aba umusenateri kugeza muri 2019. Muri 2017 yari mu basenateri basaba ko imishinga y'iterambere mu karere yakurikiranwa vuba. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/215169</ref> Yabaye umwe mu bagize komisiyo ihoraho ya Senateri ishinzwe ibibazo bya politiki n’imiyoborere myiza, maze mu 2018 yagaragaje ko ari ngombwa gutegura gahunda yo gusubiza mu buzima busanzwe abahoze ari imfungwa bahamwe n'ibyaha bya jenoside <ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/article/mukasine-appointed-chairperson-of-the-human-rights-commission</ref><ref name=":0">https://www.kigalitoday.com/kwibuka/article/urubyiruko-rurizeza-impinduka-mu-kwirinda-ingengabitekerezo-ya-jenoside</ref>

Mukasine yabaye kandi perezida w’umutwe w’u [[Rwanda]] umutwe w’abadepite bo muri [[Afurika]] barwanya ruswa (APNAC). <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/225023</ref>

Ku ya 29 Kamena 2020, Mukasine yarahiriye kuba Perezida wa Komisiyo y'igihugu ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu mu [[Rwanda]] (NHCR). <ref>http://cndp.org.rw/index.php?id=187&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=139&tx_news_pi1%5Bday%5D=30&tx_news_pi1%5Bmonth%5D=6&tx_news_pi1%5Byear%5D=2020&cHash=3200eeab2536cfa9450b7ff0d00670ff</ref> Mu Kwakira 2020, yasabye Inteko Ishinga Amategeko kongera ingengo y’imari ya NHCR no kuyiha icyicaro gihoraho i [[Kigali]] . <ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2020/10/national-rights-body-seeks-more-funding-to-execute-mandate/</ref>

